<h2 class="bold font-l">Singing In The Shower - Pitch Perfect</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Upon overhearing Beca singing in the shower, Chloe tries to force her into joining her acapella group and convinces her to sing a duet, while still in the shower. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="e82e9a" data-video-descrip="Luis goes to clean the bathroom and discovers Placido Flamingo in his bathtub, who is practicing for an opera, &amp;quot;The Bathtub of Seville,&amp;quot; and recruits Luis to join in. As Placido sings, Luis scrubs the tub in time to the music, which picks up and up as it goes along. When the song ends, Placido has Luis clean him next. " data-video-title="The Bathtub of Seville" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/e82e9a_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/e82e9a.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/SingingInTheShower" data-video-tropename="Singing in the Shower" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/SesameStreet" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/e82e9a.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">The Bathtub of ...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1hbqp6" data-video-descrip="Luna accidentally blabs about hanging with Clyde's dads while singing in the shower." data-video-title="Luna singing in the shower" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1hbqp6_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1hbqp6.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/SingingInTheShower" data-video-tropename="Singing in the Shower" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/TheLoudHouse" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1hbqp6.jpg">
